com.temp.cam.camerasdk.library.filter

Class GPUImageRGBDilationFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.temp.cam.camerasdk.library.filter.GPUImageFilter
      • com.temp.cam.camerasdk.library.filter.GPUImageFilterGroup
        • com.temp.cam.camerasdk.library.filter.GPUImageTwoPassFilter
          • com.temp.cam.camerasdk.library.filter.GPUImageTwoPassTextureSamplingFilter
            • com.temp.cam.camerasdk.library.filter.GPUImageRGBDilationFilter

  • public class GPUImageRGBDilationFilter
extends GPUImageTwoPassTextureSamplingFilter
    For each pixel, this sets it to the maximum value of each color channel in a rectangular neighborhood extending out dilationRadius pixels from the center. This extends out brighter colors, and can be used for abstraction of color images.
